-- out/todo.txt --
Error messages slightly different between v2 and v3:
- outOfBoundsDisjunction: v2 says "invalid list index 1 (out of bounds)", v3 says "index out of range [1] with length 0"
- doesNotDistributeType.a: v2 says "invalid list index \"3\" (type string)", v3 says "undefined field: \"3\""
- stringIndexToList: v2 says "invalid list index \"\" (type string)", v3 says "undefined field: \"\""
- indexOutOfBounds3: v2 says "invalid list index 4 (out of bounds)", v3 says "index out of range [4] with length 3"
